   │
 3 │ ] = base_addr
   │     ────┬────  
   │         ╰────── non-constant identifier `base_addr`
   │ 
   │ Help: `var` initializers fix the variable's address at compile time, so the right-hand side must reduce to a number; replace `base_addr` with a literal address, an arithmetic expression over literals, or a `const` that resolves to a number
